ward immediately upon his death? 2 Tim. 4 : 6-8. </div><div class="t m1d0 x18 h15 y2041 ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">6. </div><div class="t m310 x29 h15 y2041 ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Of what day was he speaking when he said that </div><div class="t m1329 x4 h15 y1658 ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">a crown should be given him &quot;at that day&quot;? Verse 1. </div><div class="t m1d2 x18 h15 yfa3 ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">7. </div><div class="t m857 x64 h15 y15d3 ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What did Paul himself say, &quot;by the word of the </div><div class="t m601 x4 h15 y1568 ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Lord,&quot; as to the only means by which Christ&apos;s followers </div><div class="t m678 x4 h15 y17a3 ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">could be with Him? 1 Thess. 4: 15-17. </div><div class="t m1d5 x18 h15 y165e ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">8. </div><div class="t m28a x29 h15 y165d ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Then when Paul, wi&quot; no choice between life and </div><div class="t mca x4 h15 y1abc ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">death, desired to be with &apos;Christ, as the best thing of </div><div class="t m3e9 x4 h15 y1b74 ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">all, for what must he have longed ?— Translation. </div><div class="t m127 x18 h15 y1a2c ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">9. </div><div class="t m3e1 x29 h15 y1ee4 ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Where else do we find Paul using similar lan-</div><div class="t m331 x4 h15 y1a2d ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">guage? 2 Cor. 5: 4. Note 1. </div><div class="t me4 x3e h15 y1ba2 ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">10. </div><div class="t m1cb x29 h15 y1d65 ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">When only will mortality be &quot;swallowed up of </div><div class="t m654 x4 h15 y16a0 ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">life&quot;? 1 Cor. 15 : 51-54. </div><div class="t me4 x3e h15 y1a9e ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">11. </div><div class="t m6bc x29 h15 y1b3c ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">For whose sake was it needful, however, that Paul </div><div class="t mdf7 x4 h15 y64e ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">should abide in the flesh? Phil. 1: 24. </div><div class="t me4 x3e h15 y1b3f ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">12. </div><div class="t mf6 x29 h15 y1e70 ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What did he therefore know that he should do? </div><div class="t md33 x4 h15 y1f06 ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Verse 25. </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
